# 🚀 HOT · CLOUD · BEACON

A futuristic neon space shooter built with pure HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Node.js.

Defend your beacon from falling hot clouds in this fast-paced arcade survival game featuring combos, level progression, and dynamic enemy spawning.

---

## 🎮 Game Overview

Three random words inspired the game:

- 🔥 **HOT** → Fire enemies (avoid them)
- ☁️ **CLOUD** → Main enemies (shoot them)
- ⭐ **BEACON** → Bonus pickups (collect for points)

You control a glowing beacon tower defending against waves of descending threats.

---

## 🕹 Controls

### Desktop
- **Move Left / Right:** Arrow Keys or A / D
- **Shoot:** Space or W / Arrow Up

### Mobile
- On-screen touch controls enabled automatically

---

## ✨ Features

- 🌌 Animated starfield background
- 💥 Explosion effects
- ✨ Combo multiplier system
- 📈 Automatic level progression
- ❤️ Lives system
- 🎇 Neon glowing cyber UI
- 📱 Fully responsive (mobile supported)
- 🏆 MongoDB leaderboard API
- 🚀 Express backend server

